    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. RH < 1 achieved at all five operating points with GCI below 5 % and validation error within pre-specified acceptance thresholds. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
